2026-01-30AAFCFarm Income Protection ActOrder Authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an Agreement with Newfoundland and Labrador to provide federal contributions to assist dairy and livestock producersOrder authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an agreement with Newfoundland and Labrador to provide federal contributions of up to $2.4 million under the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program (AgriRecovery) to assist dairy and livestock producers with the extraordinary costs incurred as a result of drought during the summer of 2025.N/A
subject: Order Authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an Agreement with Newfoundland and Labrador to provide federal contributions to assist dairy and livestock producers
precis: Order authorizing the Minister of Agriculture and Agri-Food to enter into an agreement with Newfoundland and Labrador to provide federal contributions of up to $2.4 million under the Agricultural Disaster Relief Program (AgriRecovery) to assist dairy and livestock producers with the extraordinary costs incurred as a result of drought during the summer of 2025.
